[R3] Crouse, W.H. Automobile Electrical Equipment, McGraw Hill Book Co Inc., New York
[R4] Robert N Brady, Automotive Computers and Digital Instrumentation, Areston Book Prentice Hall, Eagle Wood Cliffs, New Jersey
[R5] R.K. Jurgen, Automotive Electronics Handbook, 2nd Edition, McGraw Hill